248
00:17:58,044 --> 00:17:59,343
Hei.

249
00:18:03,917 --> 00:18:06,951
Hei, tuan!  Tunggu!

250
00:18:06,953 --> 00:18:08,853
Ini belum berakhir!

251
00:18:12,692 --> 00:18:15,660
[musik optimis]

